 p_{n,0} = u^n \\ q_{n,0} = v^n \\ p_{n,k} = u z \times q_{n-1,k-1} + u \times p_{n-1,k} \\ q_{n,k} = v z \times p_{n-1,k-1} + v \times q_{n-1,k}.
P(z, u, v) = \sum_{n\ge 0} \sum_{k\ge 0} p_{n, k} \\ Q(z, u, v) = \sum_{n\ge 0} \sum_{k\ge 0} q_{n, k}.
  \sum_{n\ge 1} \sum_{k\ge 1} p_{n,k} = P - \sum_{k\ge 1} p_{0, k} - \sum_{n\ge 1} p_{n, 0} = P - \frac{u}{1-u} \\ = u z \times Q + u \times \left(P - \sum_{n\ge 0} p_{n, 0}\right) = u z \times Q + u \times \left(P - \frac{u}{1-u}\right)
  \sum_{n\ge 1} \sum_{k\ge 1} q_{n,k} = Q - \sum_{k\ge 1} q_{0, k} - \sum_{n\ge 1} q_{n, 0} = Q - \frac{v}{1-v} \\ = v z \times P + v \times \left(Q - \sum_{n\ge 0} q_{n, 0}\right) = v z \times P + v \times \left(Q - \frac{v}{1-v}\right).
 P =  -{\frac { \left( vz-v+1 \right) u}{v-1-uv+u+u{z}^{2}v}} \quad \text{and} \quad Q = -{\frac {v \left( -u+1+uz \right) }{v-1-uv+u+u{z}^{2}v}},
 P+Q = -{\frac {2\,uzv-2\,uv+u+v}{v-1-uv+u+u{z}^{2}v}}.
 \left.(P+Q)\right|_{z=1} = -{\frac {u+v}{v-1+u}} = \sum_{q\ge 1} (u+v)^q,
 [u^m v^w] \sum_{q\ge 1} (u+v)^q = \binom{m+w}{m}.
