 \left.\left(\frac{d}{dz} (P+Q)\right)\right|_{z=1} =  2\,{\frac {uv}{ \left( v-1+u \right) ^{2}}}
 [u^m v^w] 2 uv \sum_{q\ge 0} (q+1) (u+v)^q = 2 [u^{m-1} v^{w-1}] \sum_{q\ge 0} (q+1) (u+v)^q = 2 (m+w-1)\binom{m+w-2}{m-1}.
 E[C] = \frac{2 (m+w-1)\binom{m+w-2}{m-1}}{\binom{m+w}{m}} = \frac{2mw}{m+w}.
